  "text_preview": "1 \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n  \nPRODUCT USER MANUAL \nContributors : R. Sauzède, P.R. Renosh, J. Uitz, H. Claustre  \n \nApproval Date : November 2025 \n \nFor Global Ocean 3D Chlorophyll-a concentration, \nParticulate Backscattering coefficient, Particulate \nOrganic Carbon, Photosynthetic Available Radiation \nand Downwelling Irradiance Product  \n MULTIOBS_GLO_BIO_BGC_3D_REP_015_010 \nIssue: 5.0 \n \n\n2 \n \n \n \n Product User Manual for MULTIOBS_GLO_BIO_BGC_3D_REP_015_010 \n© EU Copernicus Marine Service – Public   \nCMEMS-MOB-PUM-015-010 \nIssue 5.0 – November 2025 \n \nRECORD TABLE \n  \nIssue Date § Description of Change Author Validated By \n1.0 April 2020 All Initial version of the document R. Sauzède, H. \nClaustre \nS. Guinehut/ \nC. Derval \n2.0 January 2021  \nUpdates linked to the addition of \nthe particulate backscattering \ncoefficient parameter in the \nNetCDF files, the increase in the \nvertical resolution of the product \nand the upgrade of the method \nto derive POC \nR. Sauzède, H. \nClaustre \n \nS. Guinehut \n \n3.0 September \n2021  \nUpgraded Chl product replacing \nthe previous Uitz et al. 2006 \nparameterization method by a \nneural network-based method. \nR. Sauzède, P.R. \nRenosh, J. Uitz, H. \nClaustre \nS. Guinehut \n4.0 November \n2024  \nImprovement of Chl and \nbbp/POC estimations thanks to \nnew data available, more \naccurate Chl BGC-Argo dataset \nused for the neural network \ntraining and refined bbp to POC \nrelationship. \nR. Sauzède, P.R. \nRenosh, J. Uitz, H. \nClaustre \nH.Etienne \n5.0 November \n2025  \nReferencing Renosh et al. (2023), \na major update to the product \nnow includes new light variables \n(PAR, ED380, ED412, and ED490) \nderived at local noon using \nSOCA-light models. \nR. Sauzède, P.R. \nRenosh, J. Uitz, H. \nClaustre H.Etienne \n3 \n \n \n \n Product User Manual for MULTIOBS_GLO_BIO_BGC_3D_REP_015_010 \n© EU Copernicus Marine Service – Public   \nCMEMS-MOB-PUM-015-010 \nIssue 5.0 – November 2025 \n \nTABLE OF CONTENTS \n \nRECORD TABLE................................................................................................................................................................. 2 \nGLOSSARY AND ABBREVIATIONS ............................................................................................................................ 4 \nDATA ACCESS .................................................................................................................................................................... 5 \n1) INTRODUCTION ..................................................................................................................................................... 6 \na) Summary ............................................................................................................................................................. 6 \n2) DESCRIPTION OF THE PRODUCT SPECIFICATION ................................................................................. 7 \na) General Information ....................................................................................................................................... 7 \nb) Production System Description ................................................................................................................. 9 \nc) Dataset details ................................................................................................................................................ 10 \nd) Catalogue updating....................................................................................................................................... 11 \ne) Time averaging .............................................................................................................................................. 11 \n3) FILE FORMAT....................................................................................................................................................... 12 \n4) FILES NOMENCLATURE .................................................................................................................................. 12 \n4.1)   FILE SIZE ............................................................................................................................................................... 13 \n4.2)   STRUCTURE OF FILES ...................................................................................................................................... 13 \n5) REFERENCES ........................................................................................................................................................ 14 \n6) ANNEX..................................................................................................................................................................... 15 \na) Structure and semantic of NetCDF maps files ................................................................................... 15 \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n4 \n \n \n \n Product User Manual for MULTIOBS_GLO_BIO_BGC_3D_REP_015_010 \n© EU Copernicus Marine Service",
